{"tid":1830571,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Facebook 將習近平繙譯為「屎坑」先生  震驚世界","createTime":"2020-01-19T16:57:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T00:58:00.000Z","uid":184679,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"dbb6a271ffde6f7b582c65fc84d306e284d37da4","tid":1830571,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T16:57:49.000Z","msg":"緬甸國務資政翁山蘇姬的臉書貼文提到中國領導人習近平訪問緬甸，沒想到，臉書「自動翻譯」功能，將「習近平」姓名從緬甸文譯為英文時，卻顯示「Mr. Shithole」（屎坑先生），臉書為此出面道歉，並指是技術差錯。對此，網友紛紛笑喊，「祖克柏（札克柏格，Mark Zuckerberg）：我以前做的一切到底是為了什麼...」，更有網友歡呼，「小熊維尼」要退休了。<br />\n<br />\n根據臉書粉專「Taiwan Warm Power」今日貼文，該粉專的小編表示，在中國被嚴禁的臉書，恐怕在中國共產黨滅亡之前，都別想進軍中國市場了。甚至，臉書恐怕還會被視為「民進黨側翼」。<br />\n<br />\n除此之外，該臉書小編更欣喜歡呼，現在可以和全世界的小熊維尼迷一同歡慶，因為習近平從今以後有新稱號了，小熊維尼也自今天開始，「安全下莊」。除此之外，小編更指出，以後跟外國人介紹台灣也就更方便了，只要說「台灣不是中國的一部分，因為我們沒有叫做『Mr. Shithole』的領導人」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3045244\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3045244&d=3W3ENIgnTPsh0%2B1doSs%2BP29Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=b14e5fca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3045244&h=0807ef73\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3045244</a>"},{"pid":"2d82b303db589abf5002eb4d0ff19f8f2b98f7a2","tid":1830571,"uid":82746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T16:58:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QxshhCE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQxshhCE.jpg&h=f2dca26c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"24af093c4726dc5ddc92ecdae9fc3bd3655c6792","tid":1830571,"uid":343361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T17:04:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">嘴炮<br />\n小粉紅無反應咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"7cd31e8c65c668c4e6e649f72fc9977219a764f1","tid":1830571,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0